org.apache.poi.ss.util

Class CellReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ss.util.CellReference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord 

    public class CellReference
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenericRecord

    Common conversion functions between Excel style A1, C27 style cell references, and POI usermodel style row=0, column=0 style references. Handles sheet-based and sheet-free references as well, eg "Sheet1!A1" and "$B$72"

    Use CellReference when the concept of relative/absolute does apply (such as a cell reference in a formula). Use CellAddress when you want to refer to the location of a cell in a sheet when the concept of relative/absolute does not apply (such as the anchor location of a cell comment). CellReferences have a concept of "sheet", while CellAddresses do not.

    (Excel样式A1、C27样式单元格引用和DOE用户模型样式行=0、列=0样式引用之间的常用转换函数。还处理基于纸张和无纸张的引用，例如“Sheet 1！A1”和“$B$72”当相对/绝对概念确实适用时（例如公式中的单元格引用）使用CellReference。当相对/绝对概念不适用时，如果要引用工作表中单元格的位置（如单元格注释的锚点位置），请使用CellAddress。CellReferries有“表”的概念，而CellReferries没有。)

      • cellReferenceIsWithinRange

        public static boolean cellReferenceIsWithinRange(java.lang.String colStr,
                                                 java.lang.String rowStr,
                                                 SpreadsheetVersion ssVersion)
        Used to decide whether a name of the form "[A-Z]*[0-9]*" that appears in a formula can be interpreted as a cell reference. Names of that form can be also used for sheets and/or named ranges, and in those circumstances, the question of whether the potential cell reference is valid (in range) becomes important.

        Note - that the maximum sheet size varies across Excel versions:

        Version   File Format   Last Column   Last Row
        97-2003 BIFF8 "IV" (2^8) 65536 (2^14)
        2007 BIFF12 "XFD" (2^14) 1048576 (2^20)
        POI currently targets BIFF8 (Excel 97-2003), so the following behaviour can be observed for this method:
        Input            Result 
        "A", "1" true
        "a", "111" true
        "A", "65536" true
        "A", "65537" false
        "iv", "1" true
        "IW", "1" false
        "AAA", "1" false
        "a", "111" true
        "Sheet", "1" false
        (用于确定公式中出现的“[A-Z]*[0-9]*”形式的名称是否可以解释为单元格引用。该形式的名称也可以用于工作表和/或命名区域，在这些情况下，潜在单元格引用是否有效（在范围内）的问题变得重要。注意-最大表格大小因Excel版本而异：版本文件格式最后一列最后一行97-2003 BIFA 8“IV”（2#8）65536（2#14）2007 BIFA 12“XFD”（2#14）1048576（2#20）DOE当前针对BIFA 8（Excel 97-2003），因此该方法可以观察到以下行为：输入结果“A”、“1”真“a”、“111”真“A”、“65536”真“A”、“65537”假“iv”、“1”真“IW”、“1”假“AAA”、“1”假“a”、“111”真“表”、“1”假)
        Parameters:
        colStr - a string of only letter characters(colStr -仅由字母字符组成的字符串)
        rowStr - a string of only digit characters(rowStr -仅由数字字符组成的字符串)
        Returns:
        true if the row and col parameters are within range of a BIFF8 spreadsheet.(如果行和col参数在BIFF8电子表格的范围内，则为真。)

        public static boolean isRowWithinRange(java.lang.String rowStr,
                                       SpreadsheetVersion ssVersion)
        Determines whether rowStr is a valid row number for a given SpreadsheetVersion.(确定rowStr是否是给定数据表Version的有效行号。)
        Parameters:
        rowStr - the numeric portion of an A1-style cell reference (1-based index)(rowStr -A1风格单元格引用的数字部分（基于1的索引）)
        ssVersion - the spreadsheet version(ssVersion -电子表格版本)
        Throws:
        java.lang.NumberFormatException - if rowStr is not parseable as an integer(Java.lang. NumberSYS异常-如果rowStr不可解析为一个integer)

      • formatAsString

        public java.lang.String formatAsString(boolean includeSheetName)
        Returns a text representation of this cell reference and allows to control if the sheetname is included in the reference.

        Example return values:

        Result Comment
        A1 Cell reference without sheet
        Sheet1!A1 Standard sheet name
        'O''Brien''s Sales'!A1'  Sheet name with special characters
        (返回此单元格引用的文本表示形式，并允许控制表名称是否包含在引用中。返回值示例：结果注释A1单元格引用，没有工作表Sheet 1！A1标准表格名称“O”“Brien ''' s Sales”！A1 '带有特殊字符的工作表名称)
        Parameters:
        includeSheetName - If true and there is a sheet name set for this cell reference, the reference is prefixed with the sheet name and '!'(includeSheetName -如果为true并且为此单元格引用设置了工作表名称，则该引用将以工作表名称和'！')
        Returns:
        the text representation of this cell reference as it would appear in a formula.(此单元格引用的文本表示，正如它在公式中出现的那样。)

      • getCellRefParts

        public java.lang.String[] getCellRefParts()
        Returns the three parts of the cell reference, the Sheet name (or null if none supplied), the 1 based row number, and the A based column letter. This will not include any markers for absolute references, so use formatAsString() to properly turn references into strings.(返回单元格引用的三个部分：工作表名称（如果没有提供，则为空）、基于1的行号和基于A的列字母。这将不包括绝对引用的任何标记，因此使用formatAsString（）将引用正确地转换为字符串。)
        Returns:
        String array of { sheetName, rowString, colString }({ sheetName，rowString，colString }的字符串数组)
